ğŸ“Œ How Many Ways Can We Make a Field Required in Salesforce?
Salesforce provides multiple ways to make a field mandatory/required based on different scenarios. Below are six ways to enforce field requirements:

ğŸ”¹ 1ï¸âƒ£ At the Object Level (Field Properties)
âœ… Best for: Making the field required across all layouts, API, and automation.
âœ… How to Set:

