ğŸš€ Impact:
âœ… The field is required everywhere (Page Layout, API, Flow, Triggers).
âŒ Cannot be bypassed by automation (Trigger, API, Data Loader).

ğŸ”¹ 2ï¸âƒ£ Using Page Layouts
âœ… Best for: Making a field required only on UI (not API or automation).
âœ… How to Set:

