Select the Layout â†’ Click on the wrench (ğŸ”§) icon on the field.
Check â€œRequiredâ€ and Save.
ğŸš€ Impact:
âœ… Field is required only when editing via the UI (Record Page).
âŒ Not enforced in API, Flow, Apex, or Data Loader.

ğŸ”¹ 3ï¸âƒ£ Using Validation Rules
âœ… Best for: Making a field required conditionally (based on other field values).
âœ… How to Set:

Go to Setup â†’ Object Manager â†’ Validation Rules.
