ğŸš€ Impact:
âœ… Field is required only when using the Flow UI.
âŒ Does not enforce the requirement outside the Flow.

ğŸ”¹ 6ï¸âƒ£ Using Apex Trigger (addError)
âœ… Best for: Enforcing field requirements at the database level (before insert/update).
âœ… How to Set:

apex
Copy
