    for (Account acc : Trigger.new) {
        if (String.isBlank(acc.AccountNumber)) {
            acc.addError('Account Number is required!');
        }
    }
}
ğŸš€ Impact:
âœ… Works for API, UI, Data Loader, and Automation.
